                        "type": "section",
                        "text": "|  |  |\n| --- | --- |\n| **Spell Rank** | **Maximum Creature Level** |\n| 1st | \u20131 |\n| 2nd | 1 |\n| 3rd | 2 |\n| 4th | 3 |\n| 5th | 5 |\n| 6th | 7 |\n| 7th | 9 |\n| 8th | 11 |\n| 9th | 13 |\n| 10th | 15 |",
